title: Californication (full 2nd season)
description:
A Showtime TV series' 2nd season production created by Tom Kapinos, starring David Duchovny as Hank Moody: a troubled novelist whose move to California and his writer's block complicate the relationships with his ex-girlfriend Karen (Natascha McElhone) and daughter Becca (Madeleine Martin).

All 12 episodes of season 2 :

1)  Slip of the Tongue 	
2)  The Great Ashby 	 
3)  No Way To Treat A Lady
4)  The Raw & the Cooked
5)  Vaginatown
6)  Coke Dick & First Kick
7)  In a Lonely Place
8)  Going Down and Out in Beverly Hills
9)  La Ronde
10) In Utero
11) Blues From Laurel Canyon
12) La Petite Mort
